parameters:
Why the hell isn't the camera working since a while ago? If
I don't keep a proper watch, I'm the one who's gonna get
yelled at.

Anyway, I've got to fix the camera before the researchers
come to collect the bracelet that Lord Zagan entrusted to
us...
\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[10](Ah, there it is! The Seraphic Brace! With that...)
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[10]"Alright, if I transform now... I can recover my spiritual
power...!!"

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[6]"Ugh... It's hard to do it with my hands tied behind my
back..."
"You... How did you get this far?!"

"Come on, go back to your cell quietly! Or did you come all
this way in that outfit to give me a little 'service'?"
"It wouldn't hurt to have a little taste, right?"
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A
\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[4]I have to go get the Seraphic Breath...
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = B
Big sister... are you okay? I'll untie you now.
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]It's good that all my belongings are here in this locker.
You really saved me, thank you!

You don't need to thank me... It's my fault that big sister
ended up like this...

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]...That may be true, but you helped me like this. You seem
different from the other Liberators.

I'm just... cooperating to create a world where people can
freely use the powers they are born with. I never agreed to
do anything terrible to big sister...
\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]But you know, the Guardians are aiming for the same thing.

Eh... but the Guardians are controlling people born with
'powers'...

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]Indeed, the Guardians keep track of all people born with
'powers' and watch over them carefully.

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]But that's to prevent them from using their 'powers' to hurt
others, not to say they can't use them freely at all.

I don't understand... If we're being managed by the
Guardians, it doesn't feel like we're free...

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]The 'freedom' to hurt others takes away the 'freedom' of
those who get hurt.
\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[1]That's something I picked up from Hisana-chan♪

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]Let's cultivate 'powers' without causing trouble to others
and protect those without 'powers'... That's the rule
decided by the Guardians.
Then... why didn't the Guardians protect me...?

I was... attacked by men who had 'powers'... and afterwards,
I also awakened to my 'power'...

If the Guardians exist to protect those without 'powers',
why didn't they save me at that time!?

No matter how much I cried or screamed... no one came to
save me...

That person told me. The only way to oppose 'power' is with
'power'... That's why he said we should eliminate the
Guardians who interfere and create a world where we can
freely wield 'power'...

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[4]That's right... In the end, we can only protect what's
within our sight... That's why we need to spread the rules
further so that even those who aren't Guardians can protect
people without 'powers' and create such a world!

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[4]Using 'power' as one pleases just because it's 'freedom'...
is absolutely wrong!

...I don't know... whether that person or big sister is
right... But if big sister's 'power to protect' is
correct... then it should not lose to that person's 'power
wielded by desire'.

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[1]Of course! I'll definitely send them flying to the ends of
the stars!
Then, fight me and show me big sister's strength.
If you can't beat me, then you won't be able to beat him...

...You answered so quickly. Normally, wouldn't you hesitate
in situations like this...?

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]Is that so? When Hisana-chan and I fight, we settle it with
a battle! Isn't that normal?

Anyway... I'll be waiting in the room at the top of the
stairs ahead, so come when you're ready.

\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[0]Well, whatever. I have to win to make Amy-chan understand,
after all.
\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[4]I have to go get the Seraphic Breath...
\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[4]I have to go get the Seraphic Breath...
\PartyFace[2]\FaceIndex[4]I have to go get the Seraphic Breath...
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A

Oh, the Guardian's young lady. What are you doing in such a
deep underground place?
I go wherever there's a scent of conflict.

Then, please feel free to call on me whenever you need.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[8]As always, I wonder where she puts it all away...

As a service, I've also transferred the VR room function to
your device.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]You can even do that? Yuri-san, you're amazing.

Right, right, I've heard a little something... The Liberator
[Amy] uses the power of \C[2]『lightning』\C[0], I hear.

It seems that the ability of the Guard Drone we saw before
is based on Amy's power.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[1]That means... we have to properly prepare countermeasures...
right.

Welcome. These are the products we currently have on offer.

Oh my, aren't you cold dressed like that? I recommend using
our products to restore your spiritual power and regenerate
your robe.

...I really think wandering around dressed like that is
questionable. Please regenerate your robe quickly.

Oh, what a lovely outfit. Is that the kind of play you
prefer?
We look forward to serving you again.
It seems there are no traps in this area.
